lapcam

Purpose
The purpose of this project is to interface laptop camera and perform a variety of image recognition and processing operations on the captured face of the user.

Preparation
sudo apt-get install opencv-dev

Build:
cd build
cmake ..
make

Use:
This project is a conjuration of several tools.
face_detect_and_save - detect faces at default camera and save them at ./picutures
face_rec_train <csv.ext> <fname_trained_recogniser>
face_rec_detect - use saved trained facerecogniset to produce specific actions in responce to each individual

# detect
# train
# recognise
